<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="injury-n">injury <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ɪndʒəri/    美 /'ɪndʒəri/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(身体上的) 伤；损害；(情感上的) 伤害：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>suffer (from) an injury</strong>
负伤</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>do sb an injury / do an injury to sb
伤害某人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>head / leg / knee injury</strong> 
头部/腿部/膝盖受伤</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>personal injury</strong>
人身伤害</p></div></div>